# BreakingDown

Desktop app to log into Gmail, search/filter mails, and export breakdown spreadsheets (`.xlsx`).

## Run Locally

```bash
python3 main.py
```

## Briefcase Commands

```bash
python3 -m briefcase create
python3 -m briefcase build
python3 -m briefcase package
```
